 f(x) = \begin{cases} 0 & \text{if } -\pi < x < 0, \\  x & \text{if } 0 < x < \pi \end{cases} 
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{(2n-1)^2} = \frac{\pi^2}{8}. 
